Making sure that everyone’s a winner, the Middelburg Country Club will be running a month-long competition in the Middelburg Observer, where readers stand a chance to win a different prize each week. For week number two, a lucky reader can win a one-night stay for two people at the luxurious Middelburg Country Club Lodge.
The entry form will be published in this week’s Friday issue of the Middelburg Observer. Buy the Middelburg Observer to find out more about the next outstanding prizes on offer. Also visit the Middelburg Country Club website and Facebook page to keep up to date on all of their specials at the Middelburg Country Club bar and restaurant as well as upcoming events that are not to be missed.